## 5. Exit Gate

```
IF design document (`/planning/*-design.md`) not updated with implementation context
  → STOP. "Design document must capture implementation decisions, deviations, and context for future work."

IF implementation introduced new architectural patterns/layers not documented in architecture.md
  → STOP. "Update {{ "architecture" | instructions }} with new structural patterns that agents must follow."

IF implementation introduced new error handling patterns not documented in error-handling.md
  → STOP. "Update {{ "error-handling" | instructions }} with new error approach or classification."

{% if capabilities.hasDB %}IF implementation changed database patterns not documented in db.md
  → STOP. "Update {{ "db" | instructions }} with new schema, query, or connection patterns."
{% endif %}

{% if capabilities.hasUI %}IF implementation introduced new UI component/state patterns not documented in frontend-design.md
  → STOP. "Update {{ "frontend-design" | instructions }} with new component or architectural approach."

IF implementation introduced new styling patterns not documented in style-guide.md
  → STOP. "Update {{ "style-guide" | instructions }} with new styling conventions or approaches."
{% endif %}

IF implementation changed core functionality requiring purpose.md update
  → STOP. "Update {{ "purpose" | instructions }} with capability or boundary changes."

{% if 'docs' in commands %}

IF `{{ "docs" | cmd }}` has warnings or errors (current or pre-existing)
  → STOP
  → FIX ALL: "Doc-comments must run cleanly. Fix all errors AND warnings before proceeding."
{% endif %}

IF plan document status is not "Completed"
  → STOP. "Update plan document status."

IF test manifest status is not "Completed"
  → STOP. "Update test manifest status."

VALID: Continue to  "§5.1 Exit Checklist"
```

